  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Pilates Instructor",
  "description": "<p>At Absolute, we stand for love, family and diversity. Built on the\nfoundation of supporting personal growth - physically, mentally and emotionally - Absolute is the place where change begins. We are always looking for dynamic individuals who would like to inject their creative flair into the fitness & wellness industry!</p><p>We are looking for Senior Pilates Instructor to join our team of growing Pilates Instructors. He/ She will not only teach both group and privates classes and sessions, but also help to lead and mentor the Pilates team to achieve excellence.</p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Instruct and teach group classes across all studios;</li><li>Carry out private sessions with individual/ duet clients to help them achieve their health and fitness goals;</li><li>Recruit and mentor new instructors;</li><li>Assist to create and develop learning programme for the team;</li><li>Improve the calibre and quality of teaching across all studios;</li><li>Involve in the quarterly and yearly review of the team;</li><li>Assist in overall class planning and work with studio operations to have suitable class types and timings across all studios;</li><li>Developing new class types and conduct training to the team;</li><li>Lead, motivate and develop the team;</li><li>Be engaged with our members community, supporting and promoting events with the team;</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Fully Certified by any International Pilates body/ institution.</li><li>At least 10 years teaching Pilates, with at least 3 years leading a team of instructors.</li><li>Passionate about improving the health and movements of clients.</li><li>Trained to work with different populations, special conditions and injuries.</li><li>It would be a strong advantage if the candidate possesses certification in relation to physical therapy or physiotherapy.</li><li>Possess strong leadership and good communications skills.</li><li>Ability to develop internal programmes/ workshops.</li></ul><p><br />\nIf you think you have what it takes and would like to help clients move and live better, send in your resume!</p>",
